#!/bin/bashset -uecho ═══════════════════════════════════════════════echo  RateBridge Status — $(date +%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z)echo ═══════════════════════════════════════════════echo "echo ── Bot (systemd) ──────────────────────────────systemctl is-active ratebridge > /dev/null && echo  status : ACTIVE || echo  status : DOWNecho  uptime : $(systemctl show ratebridge --value -p ActiveEnterTimestamp | xargs -I{} date -d {} +%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S 2>/dev/null || echo N/A)echo  restarts : $(systemctl show ratebridge --value -p NRestarts)echo  memory : $(systemctl show ratebridge --value -p MemoryCurrent | numfmt --to=iec 2>/dev/null || echo N/A)echo "echo ── Redis (docker) ─────────────────────────────docker ps --filter name=trinity-redis --format  status : {{.Status}} 2>/dev/null || echo  status : MISSINGdocker exec trinity-redis redis-cli INFO stats 2>/dev/null | grep -E total_connections|total_commands | sed s/^/ / || trueecho "echo ── Nginx ──────────────────────────────────────systemctl is-active nginx > /dev/null && echo  status : ACTIVE || echo  status : DOWNecho "echo ── Resources ──────────────────────────────────echo  cpu-load : $(uptime | awk -Fload average: {print \$2} | sed s/^ //)free -h | awk /^Mem:/ { printf " memory : %s used / %s total (%.0f%%)\n", \$3, \$2, (\$3/\$2)*100 }df -h / | awk NR==2 { printf " disk : %s used / %s total (%s full)\n", \$3, \$2, \$5 }echo "echo ── Time sync (critical for trading) ──────────chronyc tracking 2>/dev/null | grep -E Reference|System time | sed s/^/ /echo "echo ── Exchanges connected ────────────────────────journalctl -u ratebridge --since 10 min ago --no-pager -o cat 2>/dev/null | grep -oP "Verified \d+ exchanges: \[[^\]]+\] | tail -1 | sed s/^/ / || echo  (check journalctl for details)echo "echo ══════════════════════════════════════════════=